interface.name: XKeySymConstants
interface.comment: TTY Functions, cleverly chosen to map to ascii, for convenience of programming, but could have been arbitrary (at the cost of lookup tables in client code.

Auxilliary Functions; note the duplicate definitions for left and right function keys; Sun keyboards and a few other manufactures have such function key groups on the left andor right sides of the keyboard. We've not found a keyboard with more than 35 function keys total.
ISO 9995 Function and Modifier Keys Byte 3 = 0xFE
